y (High = structural: bonus/split/buyback/merger; Low = routine: dividend/AGM).","why_useful":"Rising promoter & institutional ownership and clean corporate actions are confirming signals; falling promoter stake or pledging is a governance/skin-in-the-game warning.","why_it_can_fail":"Shareholding is a lagged quarterly snapshot; promoter % can fall for benign reasons (QIP, ESOP dilution). Pledge & insider detail are deferred (placeholders below)."},"snapshot":{"dimensions":{"Market":{"verdict":"negative","score":-4,"drivers":["\u2212 Below its 200-day average (-11%) \u2014 downtrend.","\u00b7 50-day average still below the 200-day (no golden cross).","\u2212 26% below its 52-week high.","\u2212 Lagging the NIFTY 500 by -6pp over 12 months.","\u2212 In a deep drawdown (-34% from its peak)."],"rule":"Points: +1 price above its 200-day average \u00b7 +1 a golden cross (50-day \u2265 200-day) \u00b7 +1 within 10% of the 52-week high \u00b7 +1 beating the NIFTY 500 over 12 months; \u22121 for each opposite, and \u22121 if more than 25% below its peak. Verdict: positive at +2 or more, negative at \u22122 or less, otherwise neutral. The Market signals (above 200-DMA, golden cross, near 52-week high, beating the index) are CORRELATED facets of ONE trend, not independent confirmations \u2014 read the Market verdict as trend-strength, not a tally of independent votes."},"Business":{"verdict":"neutral","score":1,"drivers":["\u00b7 Average quality (54/100).","\u2212 Only 0.04\u00d7 \u2014 profit not turning into cash (watch receivables/inventory).","+ Conservatively financed (D/E 0.88\u00d7, interest cover 6.1\u00d7).","+ Profit up 88% YoY (latest TTM) and accelerating."],"rule":"Points across the four business flags: +1 for each that is 'good' (quality, cash conversion, balance-sheet safety, earnings momentum), \u22121 for each that is 'weak'. Verdict: positive at +2 or more, negative at \u22122 or less."},"Valuation":{"verdict":"positive","score":2,"drivers":["+ P/E at the 4-